author: Unity
description:
Tony and Thilo from Dawn Apart's Industrial Technology and Witchcraft join Unity's Laurent for a deep dive into developing with DOTS. We'll be taking a look at Constructing Conveyor Belts & Custom Editor Tools, Voxel Materials and Destruction, Terraforming, and MORE all accomplished using ECS.

Join LIVE to ask your questions!

Check out Dawn Apart on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1866300/Dawn_Apart/
title: Developing with DOTS - Custom Tools, Voxel Physics & World Persistence in Dawn Apart
